These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, hot-chocolate, tea, 7up
There are 4 different nationalities: chinese, egyptian, thai, turkish
1. the egyptian is on the left of the chinese##1
2. the person drinking fanta is the turkish##1
3. the thai is on the right of the chinese##1
4. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the turkish##1
5. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the chinese##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |   3    |    4    |
| Beverage          | 7up | tea | hot-chocolate | fanta   |
| Nationality   | egyptian  | chinese     | thai   | turkish |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-2::.
City: london, edinburgh, berlin, paris
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: parkour, soccer, swimming, volleyball
1. the person traveling to paris is the person who's sport is soccer##1
2. the person traveling to london is on the far right##1
3. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the right of the person traveling to paris##1
4. the person traveling to paris is on the right of the person who's sport is swimming##1
5. the person who's sport is soccer is on the left of the person who's sport is parkour##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |      2      |    3    |     4      |
| City   | berlin | paris | edinburgh | london    |
| Sport   | swimming    | soccer      | parkour | volleyball |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-3::.
City: new-york, paris, rome, prague
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, drama, mystery, time-travel
1. the person watching mystery movies is on the left of the person watching time-travel movies##1
2. the person traveling to new-york is the person watching crime movies##1
3. the person watching drama movies is on the far right##1
4. the person watching time-travel movies is on the right of the person traveling to prague##1
5. the person traveling to rome is on the left of the person watching drama movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |      3      |       4       |
| City         | new-york | prague | rome   | paris |
| Movie-Genre   | crime   | mystery | time-travel | drama         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-4::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, disaster, drama, western
House: cape-cod, modern, futuristic, farmhouse
1. the modern house is the person watching western movies##1
2. the person watching disaster movies is on the left of the futuristic house##1
3. the person watching disaster movies is on the left of the person watching action movies##1
4. the person watching disaster movies is on the right of the person watching western movies##1
5. the cape-cod house is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Movie-Genre   | western | disaster | action  | drama      |
| House         | modern | farmhouse   | futuristic | cape-cod |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-5::.
4 different games are played: backgammon, poker, bridge, chess
4 different pets are kept: dog, hamster, hedgehog, pony
1. the person playing poker is on the left of the person playing backgammon##1
2. the owner of the hedgehog is on the right of the person playing bridge##1
3. the person playing chess is on the left of the owner of the pony##1
4. the owner of the hamster is on the right of the owner of the hedgehog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |  2   |    3     |      4      |
| Game   | chess | bridge | poker | backgammon |
| Pet    | dog       | pony | hedgehog | hamster     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-6::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  firefighter, designer, writer, doctor
4 different pets are kept: fish, frog, goldfish, mouse
1. the designer is on the far right##1
2. the doctor is on the left of the writer##1
3. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the owner of the frog##1
4. the owner of the fish is on the left of the writer##1
5. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the owner of the goldfish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |   3   |    4    |
| Job   | doctor | writer | firefighter | designer |
| Pet           | fish      | goldfish | mouse | frog    |

