.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-8::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  chef, designer, entrepreneur, musician
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: spy, time-travel, disaster, scientific
1. the person watching scientific movies is on the right of the designer##1
2. the person watching scientific movies is the musician##1
3. the designer is on the right of the chef##1
4. the entrepreneur is on the left of the person watching time-travel movies##1
5. the person watching spy movies is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2     |    3     |    4     |
| Job         | entrepreneur | chef      | designer | musician |
| Movie-Genre   | spy          | time-travel | disaster     | scientific    |

