.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-9::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: family, fantasy, spy, zombie
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: december, may, february, march
1. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1
2. the person watching family movies is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1
3. the person watching zombie movies is on the far right##1
4. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left of the person who's birthday is in february##1
5. the person who's birthday is in march is on the right of the person watching spy movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |   3    |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | fantasy    | spy       | family | zombie   |
| Birthday     | may | february | march   | december |

