.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-11::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, milk, sprite, water
The people use 4 different means of transport: tram, van, snowmobile, quad-bike
1. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the person driving the tram##1
2. the person driving the quad-bike is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1
3. the person drinking water is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
4. the person drinking sprite is on the far left##1
5. the person drinking milk is the person driving the snowmobile##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |       3       |   4   |
| Beverage      | sprite | milk  | hot-chocolate | water |
| Transport   | tram  | snowmobile | quad-bike           | van   |

