.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-12::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: november, september, june, may
4 different pets are kept: ferret, fish, frog, hedgehog
1. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the person who's birthday is in november##1
2. the person who's birthday is in june is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1
3. the owner of the frog is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1
4. the person who's birthday is in november is on the right of the person who's birthday is in september##1
5. the owner of the frog is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |  3   |   4    |
| Birthday   | september | november | may | june  |
| Pet           | hedgehog | fish      | frog | ferret |

