.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-13::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, juice, sprite, water
There are 4 different favourite colors: lilac, mauve, ivory, ebony
1. the person who likes ebony is the person drinking coffee##1
2. the person who likes mauve is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
3. the person drinking sprite is the person who likes ivory##1
4. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the person who likes mauve##1
5. the person drinking water is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |   2    |   3    |    4    |
| Beverage   | sprite | juice  | coffee | water   |
| Color        | ivory | mauve | ebony    | lilac |

