3. the owner of the chinchilla is the person watching horror movies##1
4. the owner of the bird is on the left of the person watching horror movies##1
5. the person watching horror movies is on the left of the person watching thriller movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |   2    |   3    |     4      |
| Pet          | snake | bird  | chinchilla  | goat |
| Movie-Genre   | fantasy   | comedy | horror | thriller   |

