.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-20::.
There are 4 different nationalities: american, argentine, mexican, nigerian
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: folk, indie, country, punk
1. the fan of folk is on the left of the argentine##1
2. the fan of indie is on the left of the nigerian##1
3. the american is on the left of the mexican##1
4. the nigerian is the fan of punk##1
5. the fan of folk is on the left of the argentine##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Nationality   | american | mexican | argentine | nigerian   |
| Music-Genre     | country  | folk    | indie       | punk |

 